# Layout Detection Benchmark: MLX vs ONNX

Comparison of layout detection performance on macOS Apple Silicon (M3 Max) using remote Muna predictors.

## Running the Benchmark

```bash
# Benchmark MLX predictor
python3 benchmarks/benchmark_layout.py "@nomic/nomic-layout-v1-mlx" "test-docs-images"

# Benchmark ONNX predictor
python3 benchmarks/benchmark_layout.py "@nomic/nomic-layout-v1" "test-docs-images"
```

## Full Benchmark Results (221 pages total)

| Document                     | Pages | ONNX    | MLX     | Speedup |
|------------------------------|-------|---------|---------|---------|
