| seney-wildlife.pdf           | 6     | 4.93s   | 1.66s   | 3.0x    |
| wwf-living-planet-2022.pdf   | 118   | 85.74s  | 20.97s  | 4.1x    |
| **Subtotal (images)**        | **142** | **113.81s** | **26.92s** | **4.2x** |
| **Technical Drawings**                                             |
| NIST-Plumbing-Drawings.pdf   | 62    | 57.80s  | 18.99s  | 3.0x    |
