## Summary Statistics

| Predictor   | Total Time  | Avg per page | Pages/sec |
|-------------|-------------|--------------|-----------|
| ONNX        | 186.82s     | 0.845s       | 1.18      |
| MLX         | 50.93s      | 0.230s       | 4.34      |
| Improvement | 3.7x faster | 3.7x faster  | 3.7x faster |

## Key Findings

- MLX processes **221 pages in 51 seconds** vs ONNX's 187 seconds
- MLX achieves **4.34 pages/second** vs ONNX's 1.18 pages/second
- Speedup varies by document type: **7.2x** (best) to **3.0x** (worst)
- Average speedup: **3.7x faster** across all document types
- Total time saved: **135.89 seconds** (2 minutes 16 seconds) on this dataset
- Both predictors run remotely on Muna's infrastructure
- MLX predictor shows best performance on wildlife/nature documents (4.2x average)
- Technical drawings show consistent 3.0x speedup
